		%p
			:markdown
				This is a beta site based on the [tog platform](http://www.toghq.com/).
				It is currently best viewed with modern browsers such as
				[Chrome](http://www.google.com/chrome),
				[Firefox](http://www.mozilla.com/firefox/)
				and [Safari](http://www.apple.com/safari/).
				Work is underway for other browsers compliance.
				The site features the [digital library](http://library.nesc.ed.ac.uk)
				prototype currently in development by the UX2 project. The library is based on a range of open source systems: 
				[Fedora](http://www.fedora-commons.org/),	[Blacklight](https://github.com/projectblacklight/blacklight),
				[Solr](http://lucene.apache.org/solr/) &amp; [Orbeon Forms](http://www.orbeon.com/)
